The evidence with the title 'GTMO by the numbers fact sheet ' says Mar 23, 2017  ... Detainees currently held at Guantánamo : 41.1. ☑ total number of detainees ever incarcerated at Guantánamo : 780.2. ☑ detainees released under president Bush : over 500.3. ☑ detainees at start of Obama presidency: 242.4. ☑ detainees transferred , repatriated or resettled under Obama: 197.5. 
